---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" active="about">
  <div class="layout">
    <main class="main">
      <div class="mono eyebrow faint">About the operator</div>
      <h1 class="serif heading">Hi, I&rsquo;m the operator behind KD3BQP.</h1>

      <div class="photo photo-placeholder">[ PHOTO &mdash; the operator at the bench ]</div>

      <p class="body-text">I&rsquo;m a Technician-class operator up in York County, Pennsylvania (grid FM19px). I got my ticket in July 2024 and got hooked fast &mdash; what started as &ldquo;I should learn this&rdquo; turned into a clipboard of pass times and a handheld that never leaves my bag.</p>
      <p class="body-text">Most of my radio time is local: the <strong>Keystone VHF Club</strong> net on Monday nights, club operating weekends like the ARRL Sweepstakes, and a growing obsession with listening to amateur satellites pass overhead. I&rsquo;m also working my way into public-service and emergency comms &mdash; the <strong>ARES / RACES / AUXCOMM</strong> side &mdash; because that&rsquo;s where the hobby meets being genuinely useful.</p>
      <p class="body-text">This blog is my logbook in public: event writeups, honest reviews of the gear I actually use (no affiliate fluff), and notes from the projects on my bench. If we&rsquo;ve worked each other, drop me a line.</p>

      <h2 class="serif subheading">What you&rsquo;ll find here</h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li>Event &amp; net writeups from the club and public-service radio</li>
        <li>Long-term reviews of the HTs and gear I actually use</li>
        <li>Field notes from satellites, contests, and bench projects</li>
      </ul>
    </main>

    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="mono panel-title accent">The station</div>
        <dl class="mono dl">
          <div class="row"><dt class="faint small">DAILY HT</dt><dd>BTech UV-PRO</dd></div>
          <div class="row"><dt class="faint small">ALSO IN THE BAG</dt><dd>Explorer QRZ-1</dd></div>
          <div class="row"><dt class="faint small">ANTENNAS</dt><dd>2m/70cm Slim Jim, mag-mount mobile</dd></div>
          <div class="row last"><dt class="faint small">BENCH</dt><dd>NanoVNA, soldering iron, too many adapters</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>

      <div class="panel">
        <div class="mono panel-title faint">Where to find me</div>
        <div class="find-me mono">
          <a href="https://www.qrz.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">QRZ &rarr; KD3BQP</a>
          <a href="https://mastodon.social/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mastodon &rarr; @kd3bqp</a>
          <a href="/contact">Email the shack</a>
        </div>
        <div class="club-note mono">Keystone VHF Club<br>Net: Mondays &middot; 2m FM</div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .layout {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 40px 0 8px;
  }
  .main {
    flex: 1 1 460px;
    min-width: 0;
    max-width: 640px;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .faint {
    color: var(--faint);
  }
  .heading {
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 38px;
    line-height: 1.12;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .photo {
    height: 260px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .body-text {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 20px;
  }
  .body-text strong {
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .subheading {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 24px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 30px 0 14px;
  }
  .list {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    padding-left: 22px;
  }
  .list li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .sidebar {
    flex: 1 1 280px;
    max-width: 320px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 24px;
  }
  .panel {
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .panel-title {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .accent {
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .dl {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .row {
    padding: 6px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .row.last {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .row dt.small {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .row dd {
    margin: 3px 0 0;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .find-me {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .find-me a {
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .find-me a:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .club-note {
    margin-top: 15px;
    padding-top: 13px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
